messages.messageBody:
I use Nero all the time, you can email me if you like. The number of pics that will fit on a CD depends on the file size and resolution. But you can fit quite a few, usually.

If you email me, put something in the subject line so I won't miss it.

Lyle

messages.messageBody:
It depends on the size of the digital photos (higher resolution takes
up more space), but in general, you should be able to fit close to 500
(the number my local camera store will put on 1 CD for $10).

--Jen
